类 HttpPost

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.uzmap.pkg.uzkit.request.Request
      • com.uzmap.pkg.uzkit.request.HttpPost
  • 直接已知子类:
    HttpPatch, HttpPut

    public class HttpPost
extends Request
    post请求。

    使用示例：

     //提交的数据
 HttpParams params = new HttpParams();
 params.addValue("key", "value");
 params.addValue("key1", "value1");
 HttpPost post = new HttpPost(url, params);
 //获取请求结果
 request.setCallback(new RequestCallback() {
        public void onFinish(final HttpResult result) {
                //TODO Log("请求结果：\n" + result.data);
        }
 });
 //发起请求
 APICloudHttpClient.instance().request(post);
